OL,3,CFormer Wales rugby league coach John
OL,4,CKear dies aged 71
OL,6,FFormer Wales rugby league coach John
OL,7,FKear has died at the age of 71.
OL,9,FThe Rugby Football League announced
OL,10,Fthat Kear died suddenly on Sunday May
OL,11,F31, on his return from covering Wigan
OL,12,FWarriors' Challenge Cup victory at
OL,13,FWembley for the BBC.
OL,15,FKear enjoyed a 10-year playing career
OL,16,Fas a threequarter with Castleford
OL,17,Fbefore embarking on his coaching
OL,18,Fcareer with Bramley in 1992.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
