OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1780413074
OL,3,CFormer Wales rugby league coach John
OL,4,CKear dies aged 71
OL,6,FHe led nine clubs across a coaching
OL,7,Fcareer lasting more than 700 matches,
OL,8,Fmasterminding a shock win for
OL,9,FSheffield Eagles in 1998 and then
OL,10,Fsteering Hull FC to glory in 2005.
OL,12,FIn July 2014 Kear took over the role
OL,13,Fas head coach of Wales until July
OL,14,F2025, succeeding Iestyn Harris.
OL,16,FHe led Wales to winning the European
OL,17,FChampionship in 2015.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
