OL,3,CFormer Wales rugby league coach John
OL,4,CKear dies aged 71
OL,6,FNigel Wood, chair of the RFL said: "On
OL,7,Fbehalf of the whole sport, our
OL,8,Fthoughts and condolences are with
OL,9,FJohn's wife Dawn, his family and with
OL,10,Fthose who played or worked alongside
OL,11,Fhim over the last 50 years.
