OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1780413074
OL,3,CFormer Wales rugby league coach John
OL,4,CKear dies aged 71
OL,6,F"Having had a 10-year career at
OL,7,FCastleford, he found his passion for
OL,8,Fcoaching which saw him oversee more
OL,9,Fthan 700 games across a career which
OL,10,Fincluded coaching England in the 2000
OL,11,FWorld Cup, Wales in the 2017 and 2021
OL,12,FWorld Cup, oversaw Challenge Cup
OL,13,Fvictories at Sheffield Eagles and Hull
OL,14,FFC, and most recently took Batley
OL,15,FBulldogs to the Championship Grand
OL,16,FFinal.
OL,18,F"But John was also an excellent
OL,19,Fbroadcast summariser with a great turn
OL,20,Fof phrase and an undiluted love and
OL,21,Fpositivity for the sport.
OL,26,@nD@AOUzD@AOU
