OL,3,CFormer Wales rugby league coach John
OL,4,CKear dies aged 71
OL,6,F"It was always a pleasure to see John,
OL,7,Fat Wakefield Trinity games most
OL,8,Frecently, as he was full of energy and
OL,9,Fenthusiasm for the game he clearly
OL,10,Floved and had given him so much, in
OL,11,Fthe same way he had given back."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
